ts = time signature 6/8

'hihat   = drums [o.t.t.x.tXt.] on ts
'ride    = drums [o . . x .X. ] on ts with rd in .ox, bd in o, sn in x ' Default hh in .ox, bd in o, sn in x

'hihatStraight = drums |XxxXxx| on ts with hh
'drumsStraight = drums |o . . x .x. | on ts with bd, sn  
'straight = drums hihatStraight + drumStraight

ride       = drumpattern [X.x.x.X.x.x.] with x=ride on ts 
hihat      = drumpattern [X.x.x.X.x.x.] with x=hihat on ts
theRhythm  = drumpattern [o.....x..x..] with o=bassdrum x=snare on ts
hihatpedal = drumpattern [x.....x.....] with x=hihatpedal on ts



